PrecisAppointment of WAYNE WOUTERS, of Ottawa, Ontario, as Deputy Minister of Human Resources Development, to hold office during pleasure; designation of WAYNE WOUTERS as Deputy Minister of Labour; and appointment of WAYNE WOUTERS as a commissioner of the Canada Employment Insurance Commission, to be the Chairperson of the Commission; effective May 13, 2002.
